name: Vessels 189: Lone Star
description:
One of the surlier members of the Hover Skater Girl Gang.  Lone Star spends her days hanging out alone in the clouds perfecting her tricks.  She is without peer on her board and has practiced everyday since she could first walk.  

When she writes her memoirs as an old lady with many healed broken bones she will title the final chapter : ‘Find a thing you love and put your all into it’
